window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Neev's life is marked with castastrophes. After losing his parents and almost everything he owned, he finds refuge with his friend Aadi in Agra. Living with an old friend in a new house, busy with a new job in a new environment, revives him somewhat. And then, life happens. As he bumps into love and tries to keep running away from it, love follows him in the person of Aashi - a small-town girl with larger than life aspirations and a novel dream. Neev sets out to fulfil her dream, but there is a price to pay. Either love, or life. What will he choose to let go? </p><p><i>When You Became My Life</i> is a story spun by destiny. It is a story of a young boy who takes it upon himself to defeat all odds and be at one with love. </p>"; 
